10
00:00:34,350 --> 00:00:37,030
<i>Why aren't I waking up?" I thought.</i>

11
00:00:38,590 --> 00:00:40,810
<i>That feeling never ended.</i>

12
00:00:45,890 --> 00:00:48,820
<i>It still hasn't ended.</i>

