For three weeks?

18
00:00:58,780 --> 00:01:02,110
It's not too far, but we can't 
get there via helicopter.

19
00:01:02,110 --> 00:01:03,030
You mean...

20
00:01:03,030 --> 00:01:04,120
...we take the snowcat?

21
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:05,180
Righto!

22
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:05,870
Yeah!

23
00:01:06,090 --> 00:01:07,480
We finally get to take one!

24
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:09,460
It's not particularly fun.

25
00:01:09,460 --> 00:01:10,910
They're very slow!

26
00:01:10,910 --> 00:01:14,050
We have to avoid crevasses and 
other dangerous places as we go.

27
00:01:14,050 --> 00:01:16,690
We'll be going one way, then 
have to alter course a bit...

28
00:01:17,180 --> 00:01:18,510
Kanae.

29
00:01:18,970 --> 00:01:21,260
I meant to do that! Totally meant to do that!

30
00:01:21,260 --> 00:01:24,820
You're the one always complaining about 
how annoying long hair is, aren't you?

31
00:01:21,260 --> 00:01:30,270
Please make sure to turn
the tap off after doing laundry.

32
00:01:24,820 --> 00:01:27,610
Well, it's better than when Takako 
used to cut it, at least...

33
00:01:28,660 --> 00:01:29,610
What about you?

34
00:01:37,020 --> 00:01:38,190
Can I?

35
00:01:38,850 --> 00:01:40,910
Of course! That's why we're inviting you.

36
00:01:43,210 --> 00:01:47,450
Could you give me time to think about it?

37
00:01:48,980 --> 00:01:49,950
Understood.

38
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:56,920
I thought she'd be jumping at the chance...

39
00:02:00,650 --> 00:02:05,330
The hole in the ozone layer was 
discovered during an expedition here,

40
00:02:05,330 --> 00:02:07,480
and they were the first in
the world to report it.

41
00:02:08,050 --> 00:02:13,020
These weather balloons 
are released twice a day,

42
00:02:13,020 --> 00:02:16,490
simultaneously, at places all over the world.

43
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:20,740
Three, two, one. Release!

44
00:02:31,470 --> 00:02:34,250
Shirase-san didn't come, did she?

45
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:37,430
She probably needs time 
to be alone and think.

46
00:02:37,430 --> 00:02:41,260
She hasn't had much to say since 
the captain made the offer...

47
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,020
It's here.

48
00:02:49,660 --> 00:02:51,770
This is the point where 
we lost communication.

49
00:02:53,610 --> 00:02:57,230
To: Mom

