51
00:02:53,610 --> 00:02:57,230
Dear Mom

52
00:02:53,610 --> 00:02:57,230
Sent from myPhone

53
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:01,100
The ridge snack station is back in business!

54
00:03:01,100 --> 00:03:02,200
Any beers?

55
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:03,510
Right...

56
00:03:03,510 --> 00:03:04,660
Here you are!

57
00:03:04,930 --> 00:03:06,120
They're nice and cold!

58
00:03:06,930 --> 00:03:08,120
That's nice of you.

59
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,270
Thanks!

60
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,120
What's the matter?

61
00:03:14,250 --> 00:03:18,100
Nothing! We finished our 
recording, so I thought...

62
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:19,000
Oh.

63
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:21,520
Hey! It's pretty warm today, huh?

64
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:24,900
Is it? It seems a bit chilly 
for the middle of summer...

65
00:03:25,530 --> 00:03:27,040
Yeah, I guess...

66
00:03:30,310 --> 00:03:32,490
They launched a weather balloon earlier!

67
00:03:32,490 --> 00:03:33,680
Could you see it from here?

68
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,430
Yeah.

69
00:03:35,740 --> 00:03:38,340
I hear today's pick-me-up is anpan!

70
00:03:44,110 --> 00:03:45,280
What is it?

71
00:03:45,850 --> 00:03:48,050
N-Nothing...

72
00:03:48,790 --> 00:03:50,850
It's just... you know...

73
00:03:50,850 --> 00:03:51,750
How to put it...

74
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:57,750
What now?!

75
00:03:57,750 --> 00:04:00,010
That's my line.

